solve.t.sol
├─ given the contract is paused
│  └─ it should revert
└─ given the contract is not paused
   ├─ when the caller does not have the AUCTION_BIDDER_ROLE
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the caller has the AUCTION_BIDDER_ROLE
      ├─ it should call the Auction contract bid function
      ├─ it should successfully solve the bid
      └─ when there is outstanding asset out balance after solving the bid
         └─ it should transfer the oustanding asset out balance to the asset out receiver
